partnerDetails.about: "NATIONAL CABLES" has established a formidable presence in the telecommunication, electric wires and cables industry. A track record of high growth and profitability in a short time is its hallmark. Its four plants produce a distinguish range which are well equipped with the state of the art manufacturing equipment and technology. The Company's principal customers are from advanced markets of the globe due to its focus on quality and safety.
